c ones"},{"d":"तेषाम्","m":"those"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"among the Vanaras"},{"d":"सेनापतिः","m":"army chief"},{"d":"कः","m":"who"},{"d":"तच्च","m":"all these"},{"d":"यथातत्त्वम्","m":"their matters"},{"d":"ज्ञात्वाशीघ्रम्","m":"knowing quickly"},{"d":"अगन्तुम्","m":"you return"},{"d":"अर्हथः","m":"fit."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"इतिप्रतिसमादिष्टौराक्षसौशुकसारणौ ।हरिरूपधरौवीरौप्रविष्टौवानरंबलम्","trans":"Having accepted the order, both the Rakshasa heroes, Suka and Saarana took the form of Vanaras and entered the Vanara army.","words":[{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"प्रतिसमाधिष्टौ","m":"having accepted the order"},{"d":"वीरौ","m":"heroes"},{"d":"शुकसारणौ","m":"S uka and Saarana"},{"d":"राक्षसौ","m":"both Rakshasas"},{"d":"हरिरूपधरौ","m":"taking the form of Vanaras"},{"d":"वानरम्","m":"in to Vanaras"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"प्रविष्टौ","m":"entered."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"ततस्तद्वानरंसैन्यमचिन्त्यंरोमहर्षणम् ।सङ् ख्यातुंनाध्यगच्छेतांतदातौशुकसारणौ","trans":"There upon both Suka and Saarana did not know the numbers (of the army) at that time as they could not count the numbers from there as it could not be conceived. It caused the raising of their hair.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"there upon"},{"d":"तौ","m":"both of them"},{"d":"शुकसारणौ","m":"Suka and Saarana"},{"d":"आचिन्त्यम्","m":"that which cannot be conceived"},{"d":"रोमहर्षणम्","m":"that which caused raising of hair (stunned)"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"वानरम्","m":"Vanara's"},{"d":"सैन्यम्","m":"army"},{"d":"सङ् ख्यातुम्","m":"to count the numbers"},{"d":"तदा","m":"that time"},{"d":"नाध्यगच्छेताम्","m":"whose number could not be known (not conceived)."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"संस्थितंपर्वताग्रेषुनिर्दरेषुगुहासुच ।समुद्रस्यचतीरेषुवनेषूपवनेषुच तरमाणंचतीर्णंचतर्तुकामंचसर्वशः ।निविष्टंनिविश्चैवभीमनादंमहाबलम् तद्बलार्णवमक्षोभ्यंददृशातेनिशाचरौ ।","trans":"The ocean of army settled on the mountain summits, in caverns and caves, on the shores of the ocean, in the forests and adjoining gardens some who crossed the sea some in the process of crossing settled all over was witnessed by the Rakshasas. It was never ending and making terrific noise.","words":[{"d":"पर्वताग्रेषु","m":"on mountain summits"},{"d":"निर्दरेषु","m":"in caverns"},{"d":"गुहासुच","m":"in caves"},{"d":"समुद्रस्य","m":"ocean's"},{"d":"तीरेषु","m":"shores"},{"d":"वनेषु","m":"in forests"},{"d":"उपवनेषुच","m":"and adjoining gardens"},{"d":"स्थितम्","m":"settled"},{"d":"तरमाणम्","m":"crossing"},{"d":"तीर्णंच","m":"shores"},{"d":"तर्तुकामंच","m":"some in the process of crossing"},{"d":"सर्वशः","m":"all over"},{"d":"निविष्टम्","m":"settled"},{"d":"निविश्चे","m":"staying"},{"d":"भीमनादम्","m":"terrific noise"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"great force"},{"d":"अक्षोभ्यम्","m":"that which is never ending"},{"d":"तद्बलार्णवम्","m":"that ocean of army"},{"d":"निशाचरौ","m":"the Rakshasas"},{"d":"ददृशाते","m":"witnessed."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"संस्थितंपर्वताग्रेषुनिर्दरेषुगुहासुच ।समुद्रस्यचतीरेषुवनेषूपवनेषुच तरमाणंचतीर्णंचतर्तुकामंचसर्वशः ।निविष्टंनिविश्चैवभीमनादंमहाबलम् तद्बलार्णवमक्षोभ्यंददृशातेनिशाचरौ ।","trans":"The ocean of army settled on the mountain summits, in caverns and caves, on the shores of the ocean, in the forests and adjoining gardens some who crossed the sea some in the process of crossing settled all over was witnessed by the Rakshasas. It was never ending and making terrific noise.","words":[{"d":"पर्वताग्रेषु","m":"on mountain summits"},{"d":"निर्दरेषु","m":"in caverns"},{"d":"गुहासुच","m":"in caves"},{"d":"समुद्रस्य","m":"ocean's"},{"d":"तीरेषु","m":"shores"},{"d":"वनेषु","m":"in forests"},{"d":"उपवनेषुच","m":"and adjoining gardens"},{"d":"स्थितम्","m":"settled"},{"d":"तरमाणम्","m":"crossing"},{"d":"तीर्णंच","m":"shores"},{"d":"तर्तुकामंच","m":"some in the process of crossing"},{"d":"सर्वशः","m":"all over"},{"d":"निविष्टम्","m":"settled"},{"d":"निविश्चे","m":"staying"},{"d":"भीमनादम्","m":"terrific noise"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"great force"},{"d":"अक्षोभ्यम्","m":"that which is never ending"},{"d":"तद्बलार्णवम्","m":"that ocean of a